# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Intelinair Figma → Token Sync
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# 1. Copy this file to .env  (never commit .env)
# 2. Fill in your values below
# 3. Run: npm run sync

# Your Figma Personal Access Token
# Generate at: Figma → Account Settings → Security → Personal access tokens
# Required scope: file_variables:read
FIGMA_ACCESS_TOKEN=figd_BaiqTDbFU3-6bTyK6YGDwnEGIxSslKLLGrPBNF7Q

# Figma file key — the alphanumeric ID in your Figma file URL:
# https://www.figma.com/design/FILE_KEY/Variable-Design-System
FIGMA_FILE_KEY=your_file_key_here
